high_descs: Turn around, step forward, then turn right and walk to the kitchen counter.
Pick up the spoon in the center of the counter.
Turn around, walk forward, then turn right and walk to the table.
Place the spoon upright in the pan located near the back of the table.
Pick up the pan with the spoon in it.
Turn right and walk to the kitchen sink.
Place the pan into the sink located on the right.
anns.task_desc: Stand a spoon up in a pan and place in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and move to the counter.
Pick up the ladle from the middle of the counter.
Carry the ladle and turn around. Turn right to the brown table.
Place the ladle in the pan in the back of the brown table.
Pick up the pan from the table.
Carry the pan and turn to the right to find the sink.
Place the pan and ladle in the sink, to the left side.
anns.task_desc: Move a ladle and pan to the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the table on the right.
Put the spoon in the pan on the back of the table.
Pick up the pan from the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the pan inside of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a spoon in a pan and put the pan in the sink.
